Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.12,0:00:04.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even fate can be used as a hint for reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.25,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Seeing through the most mysterious cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:07.91,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is the first time Conan is handling a case like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:10.18,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Were you able to enjoy his facial expressions{not really right but couldn't get a better t/l} as well as his deductions?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:11.75,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.75,0:00:13.64,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:16.38,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:02:00.93,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We set off on a trip to Shirahama in Wakayama Prefecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:04.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Despite having a feeling that somebody was watching us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:06.50,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}we continued sightseeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.45,0:02:13.72,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Later, we found out that one of the five Naniwa University students that we met the day before,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:17.94,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maki Shinjo{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}, was found dead at Sandambeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:23.36,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Her wallet and her car key were missing from her belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.89,0:02:27.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the pocket of her jacket, she had work gloves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:31.53,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Also, what is the meaning of the tiny glass bottle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:35.96,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the Mr. Sour on the easel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:40.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's probably just made to look like a robbery-murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.17,0:02:43.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's most likely that this murder was committed by an acquaintance of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:44.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the killer is among us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:57.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,please tell us where you were and what you were doing
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,from 10:26 to 11:00 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you suspect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we're just verifying things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:12.98,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tatsuhiko Yura (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:12.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sketching at Shirarahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since there were a lot of tourists,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it shouldn't be hard to verify.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In your case, Mitsui{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.75,0:03:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since you were so near the scene of the crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,your alibi may not help you much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you were there sketching the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:29.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any witnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't like to be watched when I'm sketching...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:36.50,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Madoka Mitsui (21)\NNaniwa Medical University 4th year student
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I had them show me a place where there weren't too many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who told you of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She seems to have come to Shirahama often,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she knew this place very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, Miyahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at a restaurant near Engetsu Island from about 10:30 to 12:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the parking lot where a woman was standing, calling out to the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:02.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shop where Engetsu Island is in view, right?{oy.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first, I was sketching in the vacant lot where Marine Palace used to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,right inside the tunnel from the memorial hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:10.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tunnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:15.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Back there, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:18.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki was also the one who told you about the vacant lot where Marine Palace used to be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I didn't want anyone bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But somehow, I didn't feel like drawing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I went to drink a cup of coffee to refresh myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:28.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and ended up eating lunch there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you didn't get to draw much, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was sketching at the beach in the afternoon though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean the one on the way to the memorial hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:44.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But from there, you can only get a side view of Engetsu Island, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:46.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you sketch from the rocky area,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.61,0:04:48.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where you could get a frontal view of Engetsu Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to draw anything that looked like a picture postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what art is all about!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't ask such silly questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Miyahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we looked at Maki Shinjo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s caller ID records
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and found that you were the last person to call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I called her, wondering how she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since she didn't answer, I hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was at Adventure World.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:18.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From 10:26 to about 11:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I was watching the marine show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:23.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any witnesses?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't run into anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.95,0:05:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I took a picture using my digital camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to hook it up to the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can do something like that with a digital camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are pictures of Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dropping us off this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She first dropped off Kanako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, then Yura, then Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, and finally me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I took several pictures inside Adventure World.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.14,0:05:57.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I watched the seal, dolphin and orca shows, that were 30 minutes each.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, see, from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the same show we saw, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw the one that started at 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we just missed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But might it be possible that he saw the {\i1}next{\i0} orca and dolphin show?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.95,0:06:30.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, if he took a picture of the seal show from 9:30 to 10:00,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,9:30 AM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,12:00 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Seals (green boxes)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Dolphins (orange boxes)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Orcas (blue boxes)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Break (pink text)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,note: watch the highlighting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then takes the next dolphin show at 11:30,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it would serve as his alibi from 10:00 to 11:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that's an interesting deduction,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she's not the same woman we saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.35,0:06:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person we saw had braids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.42,0:06:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has a perfect alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:07:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But after taking pictures of the orca show until 11:00
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why didn't you take any pictures until 1:15?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next picture is the one you took when you saw us at 1:15, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:12.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it strange that you didn't take any pictures for over 2 hours 15 minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's because I was riding the roller coasters and having something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, there wasn't anything I wanted to take a picture of then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, stop it with the stupid questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, please let me copy the photos on your driver's licenses
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I can go verify what you just testified.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:32.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm pretty sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}that my intuition is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:37.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}what's with the pictures he took with the digital camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:41.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His laptop...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:47.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I go outside for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, but stay out of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.90,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Adventure World
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I left just a while ago, but may I go back in again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.32,0:08:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father is inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you didn't get your hand stamped when you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stamp?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's one piece of evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Down with a fever?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. That's why we're so busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:45.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why did Maki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} go to Sandambeki where Madoka{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:48.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}after she saw us at Shirahama Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:51.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Moreover, the greatest mystery yet
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:54.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}is that I still can't figure out who killed Maki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just one more time! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:08:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me ride the Adventure Coaster, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you promise to study when we get home?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will, I will, I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay then, just one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.68,0:09:15.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no way that boy's gonna study.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:24.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.91,0:09:28.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:30.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All the pieces fall into place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That person is the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:44.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure that person's the killer, but I have no proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:47.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.68,0:09:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really unusually hot today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This was a blind spot for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:03.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've found conclusive evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.88,0:10:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you the boy who came with Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you come to verify the time of the Marine Show too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.04,0:10:20.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Mouri was saying that he wanted you to check on something else too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all, Yura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was witnessed
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,sketching right through from about 9:00 to after 11:00
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by the lifeguard who was on duty at the beach park.{UTB had "life guard", but "lifeguard" seems to be the better choice}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, as for Miyahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, we were able to get testimony from the people at the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is you, Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We questioned the Orca trainer and found out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.72,0:10:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that the same members have been on duty all day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, a person that was not even there today
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was taken on your digital camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:03.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you left Adventure World once, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No use lying about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because all we have to do is use this blacklight to disclose that you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, stop pulling our leg!{checking wiktionary's definition of "horse play", it seems they used the word incorrectly; maybe reword to "stop pulling our leg", "stop fooling around" or "cut the jokes"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.88,0:11:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who told us to check on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please show me your right hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some letters have appeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.78,0:11:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, that mark is stamped on the hand of those people who want to re-enter
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when they leave Adventure World temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:39.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pictures I just showed you were edited ones I took last time I came to Adventure World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I edited them on my laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:48.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Why would you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going steady with Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right, Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:04.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you left Adventure World at around 9:50
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to see Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} who was at Sandambeki, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you stopped over at Shirahama Station on the way, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, little boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would he go from Adventure World to Shirahama Station
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that is in the opposite direction from Sandambeki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went to buy the keychain that Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the one that is on that bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sour is only sold at the shop at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when you saw Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right, Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was really surprised back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I would run into her in a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.17,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maki{\rHonorifics - Flashback\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:49.40,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Thanks again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To top things off, I run into all of you too, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't want anybody to find out that I was going out with Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially when it came to Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Yura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I went part-way to see Madoka too.{UTB had "part way" lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got to Sandambeki a little before 12:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you weren't there,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that keychain was hanging from the easel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were having lunch then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I sensed right away that you were with Fuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you threw down the bottle with sand in it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sand from Shirarahama?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I said that I wanted to take it home?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:38.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you found it, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cracked just like my broken heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.75,0:13:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you keep something so important hidden?!{maybe edit to "such a crucial thing", or nope?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's calm down a bit here, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.19,0:13:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means you took those pictures with your digital camera
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,just so that you could show your friends that you had an alibi of not being with Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?{probably best to edit in whatever honorific he normally uses for Madoka, no? -- Yep.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, almost as if I were playing a game...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.00,0:14:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you figure it out, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I was going out with her?{same deal about "going out"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you were the very first person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} called to report what had happened to Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when it would've been more natural for her to call her boyfriend Yura{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, right?{change to "to call her boyfriend/lover, Yura-san"? -- as I assume that's who "koibito" is referring to <-- It is.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, when we got to Sandambeki, you knew where Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was sketching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought maybe you had already seen her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:26.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} happened to see you together with Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.90,0:14:36.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so in order to contain the secret you decided to shut her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanki-Shirahama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What seems to be the matter, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Don't tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This must be the much talked-about Sleeping Kogoro pose!{UTB had: "Agh! Don't tell me that...! / this is the much rumored about, / "Sleeping Kogoro" pose! -- how about "the rumored Sleeping Kogoro pose?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, Fuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has absolutely nothing to do with today's incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:57.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? He's not involved?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The main point of this case
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:03.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is that the main character was switched partway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.69,0:15:05.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim of the murder
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which was supposed to have been Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was switched to Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:11.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who hated Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} for taking her lover away,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,schemed to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was scheming to kill me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And she chose Sandambeki as the place to carry out her plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, since Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had a motive to kill,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she decided to make herself an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had someone pretend to be her
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and made that person do something at Shirahama Station that would stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Does that mean she had an accomplice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} ran into us at Shirarahama,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she thought of setting us up as witnesses to her alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.61,0:15:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} asked us for our schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:16:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She set it up so that we would arrive at Shirahama Station at 10:00 today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s accomplice had other plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Other plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That plan was to switch Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s alibi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} that we saw at Shirahama Station at about 10:10 was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was an imposter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The imposter wore a wig, hat, sunglasses and even make-up{change make-up to outfit/clothes to clarify it's kako [spelling?] and not the other more common definition of make-up? :3well, he DID say a word for "cosmetics", so it's probably fine as it is, não? -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to look just like Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time we met at Shirahama Station,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:43.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the imposter had already killed Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at around 9:35 at Sandambeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,35 minutes before we met her...?{UTB had "Whaaaat?!" xD -- works for dub scripts I guess though}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.37,0:16:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Who is that imposter anyway, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is only one person whom Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} trusted enough
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to make her an accomplice in committing the murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.89,0:17:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and who could disguise herself to look just like Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} among the four of you.{UTB had "herself"...well, makes dax to me. reverted =p -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:03.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Kanako Miyahara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...only {\i1}you{\i0} could have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} already told Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} yesterday that she would not listen to Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:17.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told her to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that the police wouldn't suspect
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that Kanako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} helped her construct an alibi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because she was under Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.75,0:17:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This morning, after Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} dropped everyone off at their destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.92,0:17:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she returned to Engetsu Island, and made Kanako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} get into her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} disguised herself as Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as they drove along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she was supposed to get off at the inner alley of Sandambeki,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and after that, Kanako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would drive to Shirahama Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then after her alibi was established,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was supposed to kill Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.66,0:18:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why there were work gloves in Maki Shinjo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s jacket!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was going to use them when committing the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s plan suddenly fell apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After committing the murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s knife and wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:29.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She did this to make it look like a robbery-murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.95,0:18:32.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She then drove away in the car
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and arrived at Shirahama Station a little before we got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then she observed us
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and waited for the right time to appear before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means that when Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said that he felt as if he was being watched...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right! It was Kanako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.78,0:18:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:19:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...made us witness Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at around 10:10.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:03.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you went to Sansho Shrine, while at the same time getting rid of the evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then abandoned the car and went back to Engetsu Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.62,0:19:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any grounds for saying all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although you mentioned not wanting to be bothered by others,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you went out of your way to choose a beach with a lot of tourists and started sketching.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fearing the estimated time of death being extended later on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you called Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} on her cell phone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.41,0:19:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to make Madoka{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} find her as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nothing but a far-fetched interpretation of the facts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you insist that I'm the killer, show me proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.87,0:19:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was using make-up that she ordered from Paris, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.77,0:19:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may have been able to get a hold of the clothes that Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wore,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.40,0:19:48.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or the bags she carried, in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but as for the characteristic color lipstick that she used,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you could find no substitute here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:20:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, your saliva was found on that lipstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The saliva of the person who used it last—you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.29,0:20:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s lipstick, that you could not wipe off completely,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.59,0:20:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is still on your lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Under Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.47,0:20:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we have already received the results of the forensic analysis of Maki Shinjo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s lipstick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to explain in detail about saliva and blood type?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:33.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have that much medical knowledge myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:37.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When did you figure out that I was the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It took me quite a while to put my fingers on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only had a hunch that it was one of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I found the keychain near the dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keychain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had the key of the rental car
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,attached to the same keychain as her house keys, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the key of the rental car was missing from that keychain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because Maki...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A robber would have taken the keychain and all
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s keychain was not the hook-type,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the coil-type, that is harder to remove the key from.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.22,0:21:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I concluded that Maki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:26.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,likely handed over the car key voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very impressive, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.49,0:21:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've completely lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Kanako, why did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...entered the university illegally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked Maki's father to get me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I got in,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maki threatened to reveal what happened if I didn't listen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I kept following her orders all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be free...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...from Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:30.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Shirahama Station
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.35,0:23:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll manage to get back to Tokyo by tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.78,0:23:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's goodbye to Shirahama...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:42.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sleepy, I can't stand it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:45.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then have some of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An {\i1}umeboshi{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.66,0:23:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm awake!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now if only this could also awaken your talent as a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.35,0:24:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ray{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you're OK. Switch it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ricardo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.72,0:24:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Left, left!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:18.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This man...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:21.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Isn't he that reporter from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.02,0:24:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His left hand's latched onto something...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.25,0:24:31.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.30,0:24:36.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.50,0:24:38.11,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, for the first time in a long time, Osaka is the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.11,0:24:40.79,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanimiso{\i0}, {\i1}kaibashira{\i0} and {\i1}kaiware{\i0} are the 3 Ks of sushi!
